1.6
log
@*enty->*ently where applicable
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: srt0.s,v 1.5 2004/01/10 22:47:54 pvalchev Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: srt0.s,v 1.1 2000/08/20 14:58:42 mrg Exp $	*/

